<br>
My other concern is that I usually am grouped with a 22 beastmaster, so I tank quite a bit, as I cannot seem to evade on his pet.  My AC is around 480 or so, which I thought was not too bad for my level.  I take a beating tho, usually worse than the warder.  Would a haste item be a bad idea, as Iwill just get more aggro and thus it will be harder to evade?  I know ultimately rogues make bad tanks, as we are not a plate class, and really belong on the back side of the mob.  Should I save my pp and work on AC, for at least the next 10-20 levels?<br>
